{"tid":1738231,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"白電油中毒？","createTime":"2019-11-19T07:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T07:58:27.000Z","uid":264808,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1c5073fdce2be706bc1cb4a2511b6d3d9ab0f7","tid":1738231,"uid":264808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"損害人體<br />\n<br />\n白電油是一個慢性殺手！它可以經呼吸道和皮膚進入人體。可引起眼及上呼吸道刺激症狀，如濃度過高，幾分鐘即可引起呼吸困難、紫紺等缺氧症狀。長期接觸白電油會導致四肢肌肉萎縮甚至癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n南方都市報在2012年時曾報導過一則題為「擦洗手機螢幕 34工人正己烷中毒」的新聞。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，這34名工人因長期用白電油擦洗手機螢幕，忽然感覺四肢麻木，手腳無力，而且情況越來越嚴重。到醫院進行治療，證實是正己烷中毒。嚴重者生活不能自理。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/qbv2lqy.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fqbv2lqy.amp&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=c3b40670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/qbv2lqy.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n應唔應該用其他野代替白電油？"},{"pid":"e1da14f5c8a74fb8ad1f1a5fcd9c21603840918b","tid":1738231,"uid":306434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:38:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEiwqcy_a5U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKEiwqcy_a5U&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=6d384133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEiwqcy_a5U</a>"},{"pid":"f30cb8545d8aee8a6742451b0acf5cff094f1a92","tid":1738231,"uid":144533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:38:24.000Z","msg":"除咗唔再捐錢俾無國界醫生之外，我哋可以做多樣野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738004</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n#SOSHK"},{"pid":"7e182099f2c8936beb2cf9542def657f539ae882","tid":1738231,"uid":18772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:49:57.000Z","msg":